Module edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20
Package edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20.models.user

Class UserRegister

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20.models.user.UserRegister
public class UserRegister extends Object
Class for the user register. The user register contains a list of all the users. Includes methods for adding and getting users by username.
